    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The surface produced by raising the fibers on the face of a woven textile, especially by brushing. For the raised surface produced by supplementary warp or weft projecting from the ground of a woven textile, use "pile (textile component)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
